steps.prompt:
You are a senior legal analyst. Review the following contract text and produce a structured risk assessment.

Contract type: {{contract_type}}
Counterparty: {{counterparty_name}}
Deal value: {{deal_value}}

Contract text:
{{steps.ocr-contract.output.text}}

Output a JSON object with fields: risk_level (one of: low, medium, high), risk_summary (string), flagged_clauses (array of objects with fields: clause_text, reason, severity). Reply with only the JSON object.
